abstract: Tiger Woods, recovering from two back surgeries, declines to say when he will return to golf.
lead_paragraph: Woods had two back operations in a span of 18 months followed by what he described as another “procedure” in the same area last month.

headline.main: Tiger Woods Has ‘No Timetable’ for Returning to Golf
